data.description: Wonderful detached colonial on a cul-de-sac in Bulle Rock! Main floor primary bedroom suite with laundry on the main floor. Large formal sitting and dining spaces. Beautifully open kitchen and family room areas with vaulted ceilings and sliders to rear deck with glimpses of the Chesapeake Bay. Upstairs you'll find 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths (one bedroom has an en-suite bathroom.) The lower level is finished and features a large wet-bar and walk-out to a rear patio. Attached side-entry garage. This home has it all! Community covers lawn care, snow removal to your door and you'll have access to the Residents' Club with an indoor and outdoor pool, tennis courts, full gym, billiards room, walking trails and much more! Residents receive discounts at Bulle Rock Golf as well.
